HEADWORD: Grouser
<hw>Grou"ser</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(<er>Dredging</er>,
<er>Pile Driving</er>, <it>etc.</it>)</fld> <def>A pointed timber
attached to a boat and sliding vertically, to thrust into the ground as
a means of anchorage.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

